---
title: Tuscan-Style Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Simplicity goes a long way in a dish, take this one here - seared chicken in a herby Tuscan seasoning and a roast
veggie toss. That’s all you need to experience a medley of flavour and if you like (which we know you will), drizzle
over a creamy pesto sauce.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
